OL,3,CCardiff's new indoor arena gets final
OL,4,Cgo-ahead ahead of planned opening in
OL,5,C2028
OL,7,FPlans for Cardiff's 16,500-capacity
OL,8,Findoor arena have taken a major step
OL,9,Fforward ahead of its planned opening
OL,10,Fin three years.
OL,12,FCardiff Council and the consortium
OL,13,Fbehind the proejct - made up of Live
OL,14,FNation and Robertson Property - have
OL,15,Fannounced financial close on the
OL,16,Fproject.
