OL,3,CCardiff's new indoor arena gets final
OL,4,Cgo-ahead ahead of planned opening in
OL,5,C2028
OL,7,FSet to open in 2028 in Cardiff Bay,
OL,8,Fthe new arena is forecast to provide
OL,9,Fan economic boost for Cardiff and is
OL,10,Fexpected to create more than 1,000
OL,11,Fjobs.
OL,13,FMcLaren Construction has been
OL,14,Fappointed as the main contractor, and
OL,15,Fdevelopers say the scheme will focus
OL,16,Fon sustainability and local employment
OL,17,Fopportunities throughout construction
OL,18,Fand once the arena is operational.
