OL,7,FCardiff Council leader Huw Thomas
OL,8,Fsaid: "This arena will transform
OL,9,FCardiff's visitor economy in a way
OL,10,Fnothing has since the stadium opened
OL,11,Fin 1999. It's not just about the
OL,12,Fbricks and mortar; it's about
OL,13,Funderpinning and enhancing Cardiff's
OL,14,Fstatus as a vibrant, dynamic
OL,15,Fdestination for music and culture.
