OL,7,F"But crucially, this project will
OL,8,Fdrive economic growth and social
OL,9,Fvalue, particularly in the area
OL,10,Fsurrounding the arena, creating jobs
OL,11,Fand lifting horizons in some of Wales'
OL,12,Fmost economically-challenged
OL,13,Fcommunities."
OL,15,FUK Government business and trade
OL,16,Fsecretary Jonathan Reynolds called the
OL,17,Fmove "another clear vote of
